Package ti

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DocumentProcessor
    This interface defines methods to parse and process the text from documents of a particular tipe (eg, html or text).
    RetrievalModel
    This interface defines methods implemented by a retrieval model.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Batch
    This class contains the logic to run the retrieval process of the search engine in batch mode.
    Cosine
    Implements retrieval in a vector space with the cosine similarity function and a TFxIDF weight formulation.
    CosineWithFeedback
    Implements retrieval in a vector space with the cosine similarity function and a TFxIDF weight formulation, plus pseudorelevance feedback.
    HtmlProcessor
    A processor to extract terms from HTML documents.
    Index
    This class represents the index of the search engine.
    Indexer
    This class contains the logic to run the indexing process of the search engine.
    Interactive
    This class contains the logic to run the retrieval process of the search engine in interactive mode.
    SearchEngine
    This class is the main entry point to run the search engine.
    SimpleProcessor
    A very simple document processor.
    Tuple<T1,T2>
    This class represents a tuple of two items.
